To select an event, you can use the `handleSelectEvent` function, which takes in an event object and selects it from the `events` array based on the `category` attribute. The `selectedEvent` variable will hold the selected event if the user selects an event type.
To submit the form, you can use the `handleSubmit` function, which takes in the `event` object and adds it to the `filteredEvents` array. The `handleFavoriteEvent` function will be called to save the selected event as a favorite event.
